`8Keywords``   : Saves_Vs_Spell
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

This statistic represents your "will power". Like AC, somewhat confusingly, the
lower this is, the better. The better it is, the more likely your spells are to
take effect on others, the more likely you are to resist the spells of others,
and the more damage your magic will do.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
